      <list type="simple">
         <item>GB (2007-10-18): a problem. One example above seems to be suggesting that the
            <tag>space</tag> is an abbreviation marker. I'm not sure I understand this, and in any
            case it would be illegal to tag thus in P5 (from where we have borrowed the
            <tag>am</tag> element). I have eliminated the old example until we can figure out what 
            we meant by this issue.</item>
      </list>
